title: Authorizes assistant corporation counsel or assistant county attorney to issue subpoenas duces tecum prior to juvenile delinquency proceeding
summary: Authorizes the assistant corporation counsel or assistant county attorney, within a presentment agency, to issue subpoenas duces tecum for records prior to the origination of a juvenile delinquency proceeding, when such records are necessary for the preparation or filing of a petition to commence such proceeding.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the family court act, in relation to the issuance of subpoenas duces tecum in juvenile delinquency cases
